      • registerOrGetDimension

        public static DimensionType registerOrGetDimension(ResourceLocation name,
                                                   ModDimension type,
                                                   PacketBuffer data,
                                                   boolean hasSkyLight)
        Register or get the existing dimension type for the given dimtype name. Dimensions already known to the save are loaded into the DimensionType map before the RegisterDimensionsEvent is fired. You can use this helper to get your existing dimension, or create it if it is not found.
        参数:
        name - Registry name
        type - ModDimension type data
        data - Extra data for the ModDimension
        hasSkyLight - does this dimension have a skylight?
        返回:
        the DimensionType for the dimension.

      • registerDimension

        public static DimensionType registerDimension(ResourceLocation name,
                                              ModDimension type,
                                              PacketBuffer data,
                                              boolean hasSkyLight)
        Registers a real unique dimension, Should be called on server init, or when the dimension is created. On the client, the list will be reset/reloaded every time a InternalServer is refreshed. Forge will save this data and keep track of registered values, syncing automatically from the remote server.
        参数:
        name - Registry name for this new dimension.
        type - Dimension Type.
        data - Configuration data for this dimension, passed into
        hasSkyLight - skylight for this dimension
        返回:
        the DimensionType for the dimension.

      • keepLoaded

        public static boolean keepLoaded(DimensionType dim,
                                 boolean value)
        Configures if the dimension will stay loaded in memory even if all chunks are unloaded.
        参数:
        dim - The dimension
        value - True to keep loaded, false to allow unloading
        返回:
        The old value for this dimension.

      • keepLoaded

        public static boolean keepLoaded(DimensionType dim)
        Determines if the dimension will stay loaded in memory even if all chunks are unloaded.
        参数:
        dim - The dimension
        返回:
        True if the dimension will stay loaded with no chunks loaded.

      • getWorld

        public static ServerWorld getWorld(MinecraftServer server,
                                   DimensionType dim,
                                   boolean resetUnloadDelay,
                                   boolean forceLoad)
        Retrieves the world from the server allowing for null return, and optionally resetting it's unload timer.
        参数:
        server - The server that controls this world.
        dim - Dimension to load.
        resetUnloadDelay - True to reset the unload timer, which is a delay that is used to prevent constant world loading/unloading cycle.
        forceLoad - True to attempt to load the dimension if the server has it unloaded.
        返回:
        The world, null if unloaded and not loadable.
